data.title: Carrie A. Lara, Psy.D. – Clinical Psychologist & Children Book Author
data.text: I am an author located in Sonoma County, Ca. I enjoy writing and have multiple published children’s books. My books and story writing tend to focus on social, emotional, and cultural development. I have three published picture books and one upper elementary grade book which have won awards in multiple areas. I truly enjoy the art and expression of the written word and in addition to writing, I offer consultation and editorial services for other authors. Please click the below links for further details of my books, future projects, and services.
